skasse.", "Grendahl giftet seg i 1810 med Bereth Husdahl fra Geitastrand. Det fins ikke noe bilde av Michel Grendahl; det stred mot haugianernes livssyn \u00e5 bli \u00abforeviget\u00bb."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "nyheter|trondheim|byens gater"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "afd1e4e94b88169497de8d6b158729a6b76a43c2c9e1dc466b468bc0b05c9089"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-30T15:39:00.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Michel Grendahl var haugianer, bonde, politiker og forretningsmann."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1151933.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Michel-Grendahls-veg_ny"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/9e529f7b9f03339eac06b0e9549376f72a2c0004.jpg?599ade9c"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Gjorde Havstein til m\u00f8nsterg\u00e5rd -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "9e529f7b9f03339eac06b0e9549376f72a2c0004"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "byens gater", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["m\u00f8nsterg\u00e5rd", "g\u00e5rden", "kirke"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["grendahl", "havstein", "by\u00e5sen", "lademoen", "grendal", "geitastrand", "bereth husdahl", "s\u00f8ndre trondhjems", "m\u00f8re", "hans nielsen hauge", "kvernes"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["rennebu", "drammen", "bergen", "kristiansund", "aver\u00f8y"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field":